Class OrthantNeighborhoodGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • mpmToolbox.supplementary.orthantNeighborhoodGraph.OrthantNeighborhoodGraph
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ScorePage
    public class OrthantNeighborhoodGraph
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an implementation of Tobias Germer's Orthant Neighborhood Graph for 2D. The algorithms, however, are different.
